Payload.QuestionText: Rate each member of your team on the degree to which he or she has needed your assistance or the assistance of others to complete assigned work.  In addition to rating your teammates, you should also assess yourself where you see your own name. You do not need to rate any individual on this list who either didn't have responsibilities on your team for this sprint, or whom you didn't work closely enough with to be able to assess their contributions.
